message.content: I can provide information and entertainment, but I can't currently take actions on your behalf. For example, I can plan a custom travel itinerary, but I can't buy tickets or book hotels. I can write you an email, but I can't send it. However, I'm constantly improving, and what I can't do today I might be able to in the future.
